        {
            "name": "Giant Solifugid",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [],
            "text": "The smallest of giant solifugids are still large enough to harry desert traders and their mounts.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Animal</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 15",
